The terms ``reclamation plan'' or ``site reclamation plan'' means a plan approved by NRC or an Agreement State that
establishes the work necessary to comply with UMTRCA or where appropriate applicable Agreement State requirements.


The term ``remedial action'' means decontamination, decommissioning, reclamation, and other remedial action
at an active uranium or thorium processing site. 

The term ``Secretary'' means the Secretary of Energy or her designees. 

The term ``site owner'' is defined as a person that presently holds, or held in the past, any interest in land, including
